OL,4,G0720FThe Big Match Revisited
OL,5,     GJoin Brian Moore as Spurs come up
OL,6,     Gagainst a stubborn Sunderland
OL,7,     Gside in April 1978, West Ham
OL,8,     Gtravel up to the northwest to
OL,9,     Gtake on Manchester United, and
OL,10,     GArsenal face Leeds United.
OL,11,G0825FThe Sweeney
OL,12,     GMoney, Money, Money: Police drama
OL,13,     Gseries. Eddie Monk wins the
OL,14,     Gpools, but then receives
OL,15,     Gblackmail threats about the part
OL,16,     Ghe played in a robbery.
OL,17,G0930FITV Racing: The Opening Show
OL,18,     GOli Bell and the team are at
OL,19,     GDoncaster on the first day of the
OL,20,     Gflat season.
